---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Play"
  description="Fun interactive tools and games. Test your SEO intuition, generate halftone art, and quiz your Google algorithm knowledge."
  currentSlug="play"
>
  <div class="note-content">
    <h1>ðŸŽ® play</h1>

    <p>fun stuff I've built. more coming.</p>

    <div class="activity-cards">
      <a href="/play/keywords" class="activity-card">
        <span class="activity-number">01</span>
        <div class="activity-info">
          <h2>seo intuition test</h2>
          <p>guess which keyword has higher search volume. 10 rounds, trust your gut.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/play/halftone" class="activity-card">
        <span class="activity-number">02</span>
        <div class="activity-info">
          <h2>halftone generator</h2>
          <p>convert any image to halftone dots or ASCII art. download or animate.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/play/updates" class="activity-card">
        <span class="activity-number">03</span>
        <div class="activity-info">
          <h2>name that google update</h2>
          <p>guess the algorithm update from its description. test your seo history.</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .activity-cards {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .activity-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }

    .activity-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--amber-accent);
      background: var(--amber-bg-subtle);
    }

    .activity-number {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace);
      min-width: 24px;
    }

    .activity-info h2 {
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .activity-info p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
